				<div class="et_pb_text_inner"><h3>Improved synchronization</h3>
<p>Synchronize and update your inbox, calendar and contacts in real-time across all your devices the way it should be. <a href="/enterprise-email/"><span class="more">L</span>Learn more</a></p></div>
